-- Account Computer with Radar + Deposit + Rednet Transfer + Background Support
-- Added:
--   - Local gambling win stats tracking on this account computer
--   - Stores stats in /winStats.json
--   - Tracks only positive winning profit
--   - Roulette stats are calculated as:
--       total payout for the spin - total amount bet that spin
--   - Losses do not subtract from leaderboard
--   - Slot direct gamble_win_stat messages are tracked
--   - Public chat command support through manipulator_41:
--       wc casino stats
--   - Listens for BOTH:
--       chat_capture: hidden/captured commands
--       chat_message: normal visible chat messages from anyone
--   - Replies publicly with one compact chat.say(message)
--   - Allows hiding certain players from public casino stats

-- =========================================================
-- === Top Config
-- =========================================================

